== Scientists associated with the IHES == [[Alain Connes]] (Fields Medal 1982), has been holding the Léon Motchane Chair since 1979. Several [[Centre national de la recherche scientifique|CNRS]] researchers are also based at the IHES: [[Ahmed Abbes]], Cédric Deffayet, [[Ofer Gabber]], [[Fanny Kassel]], and [[Christophe Soulé]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ihes.fr/en/scholars/professors|title=IHES Faculty|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=}}</ref>
